WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.200 --> 00:00:02.000
Young Master Yan

2
00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:03.560
You said it.

3
00:00:03.560 --> 00:00:05.860
It has nothing to do with you whether I divorce or not

4
00:00:15.880 --> 00:00:16.860
So late

5
00:00:17.400 --> 00:00:18.540
Where have you been?

6
00:00:18.880 --> 00:00:21.820
Fu Tingchuan, we are divorced

7
00:00:22.760 --> 00:00:24.900
It's not up to you where I go

8
00:00:25.120 --> 00:00:26.840
We are not officially divorced yet.

9
00:00:26.840 --> 00:00:28.560
You are still my wife

10
00:00:28.560 --> 00:00:29.932
If you do something

11
00:00:29.932 --> 00:00:31.066
Insulting the Fu family

12
00:00:31.066 --> 00:00:32.420
It will discredit us.

13
00:00:34.160 --> 00:00:34.980
Ah!

14
00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:37.620
So that's what you care about

15
00:00:38.760 --> 00:00:39.900
Your clothes.

16
00:00:40.600 --> 00:00:41.800
You and Bo Siyan

17
00:00:41.800 --> 00:00:43.240
I've been kidnapped.

18
00:00:43.240 --> 00:00:44.433
It was saved by Yanshao

19
00:00:44.433 --> 00:00:45.900
You were kidnapped

20
00:00:46.960 --> 00:00:47.980
Are you all right?

21
00:00:48.720 --> 00:00:50.900
You keep saying that I am your wife

22
00:00:51.040 --> 00:00:53.460
You don't even know that I was kidnapped

23
00:00:53.720 --> 00:00:55.620
Have you ever cared about me?

24
00:00:58.280 --> 00:00:59.820
I'm tired, you can go

25
00:01:00.160 --> 00:01:01.820
I'll get someone to change the locks tomorrow

26
00:01:02.080 --> 00:01:04.166
Don't look for me without authorization

27
00:01:04.166 --> 00:01:04.700
Qu Yan

28
00:01:05.240 --> 00:01:06.900
I've been waiting for you for a long time today.

29
00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:07.800
OK

30
00:01:08.320 --> 00:01:09.300
So what?

31
00:01:12.040 --> 00:01:14.866
I thought a lot while I was waiting for you

32
00:01:14.866 --> 00:01:15.380
I think

33
00:01:16.720 --> 00:01:18.820
Maybe we can get to know each other again

